  "detailed_description": "<h1>Another SteamWorld Game is out! Play Now!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.poster.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.webm?t=1726132166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.mp4?t=1726132166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>SteamWorld Heist</strong>, you command a steam-driven pirate crew in a series of epic tactical shootouts. It’s turn-based strategy with a twist: You manually aim the guns of your robots, allowing for insane skill shots and bullet-bouncing action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/0f44c25545031cbfdbb25eee7931f106.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=335 /></span><br><br>As the captain you will board, loot and shoot your way through enemy spaceships. Overcome the challenges of the vast frontier by upgrading your recruits with unique abilities, weapons – and even stylish hats!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/9fe9aaa3d1b6c10a19658b6d6c5b2c83.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategy focused on skill rather than chance<br></li><li>Procedurally generated levels<br></li><li>15-20 hours of playtime, followed by New Game+<br></li><li>Kind to newcomers, deep and challenging for veterans<br></li><li>Soundtrack by Steam Powered Giraffe</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.poster.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.webm?t=1726132166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/def64e27bdf9e4e27b2ad4668489671b.mp4?t=1726132166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>SteamWorld Heist</strong>, you command a steam-driven pirate crew in a series of epic tactical shootouts. It’s turn-based strategy with a twist: You manually aim the guns of your robots, allowing for insane skill shots and bullet-bouncing action!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/0f44c25545031cbfdbb25eee7931f106.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=335 /></span><br><br>As the captain you will board, loot and shoot your way through enemy spaceships. Overcome the challenges of the vast frontier by upgrading your recruits with unique abilities, weapons – and even stylish hats!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/322190/extras/9fe9aaa3d1b6c10a19658b6d6c5b2c83.avif?t=1726132166\" width=616 height=78 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategy focused on skill rather than chance<br></li><li>Procedurally generated levels<br></li><li>15-20 hours of playtime, followed by New Game+<br></li><li>Kind to newcomers, deep and challenging for veterans<br></li><li>Soundtrack by Steam Powered Giraffe</li></ul>",
